This bot can be altered to purchase any "hype" item on any given release day. 

Improvements that can be made:

- have the algorithm self deploy at exactly 1s after the drop time (after 1s to ensure that we will not be denied purchase
due to different clock synchronizations on the company's server)

- create a better method to bypass the captcha; This algorithm merely allocates time for the user to manually complete the
captcha.

